data.description: Welcome home to this hidden gem in tranquil Palmetto, Georgia. This home features a family room with a vaulted ceiling, a galley kitchen design layout with new stainless steel appliances, and a separate breakfast room. Enjoy the much sought after master bedroom on the main floor that has a bathroom with a separate soaking tub and shower. Two spacious secondary bedrooms and a full bath complete the upper level. The home has luxury vinyl plank throughout and has been freshly painted. Enjoy a private backyard and attached shed for storage. This home is move-in ready. Schedule your showing today!
